{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_03_01",
  "title": "兵藤雫 1話 意外な選択",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "雫、この間話したソロデビューの件、考えてくれたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ have you thought about the solo debut we discussed recently?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい……\nやっぱりソロは無理……自信、無い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry…\nI think… a solo is too much… I don't have the confidence…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "でも歌うのは好き……\n{user}さんの期待にも応えたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I love singing…\nI want to meet {user}-san's expectations too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "それで考えた……一人じゃなければ……\n一緒に歌ってくれる人がいたら出来る……かも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I thought… maybe if I'm not alone…\nIf there's someone to sing with me‚ I might be able to do it… maybe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ツインボーカルか……雫自身の気持ちも大事だしな\n誰か一緒にやりたい相手はいるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Twin vocals‚ huh… Shizuku's feelings are important too.\nDo you have someone in mind you'd want to do this with?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "……天動瑠依さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rui Tendo-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "天動さん？\n意外だな、てっきりサニピか月ストの誰かかと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tendo-san?\nAn Unexpected Choice. I thought it might be someone from Sunny Peace or Moon Tempest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "……ダメ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Is it not good?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いや、ダメじゃないよ\nただ天動さんが引き受けてくれるかどうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's not that.\nJust wondering if Tendo-san would be willing to accept…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "そこが問題……瑠依さんは、トリエル以外のユニット\nやりたがらないかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The problem is… I'm not sure if Rui-san would want to be\nin a unit outside of TRINITYAiLE…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "だから……\nどうすれば瑠依さんを説得出来るか、教えてほしい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So…\nI was wondering how I could convince Rui-san… Can you give me some advice…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、そう簡単には思いつかないが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's hard to say…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、雫はアイドルに詳しいから\n天動さんのことなら俺よりよく知ってるんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But since you're knowledgeable about idols‚\nperhaps you know more about Tendo-san than I do‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん……アイドルの知識なら誰にも負けない……\n瑠依さんのプロフィール……全部頭に入ってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course… When it comes to idol knowledge‚ I won't lose to anyone…\nI have memorized Rui-san's entire profile…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "その知識を利用してみたらどうだ？　俺の考えよりも\n自分で考えた言葉の方が相手の心に響くと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about using that knowledge? I believe words\nyou've thought of yourself will resonate more than what I suggest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "私のアイドル知識で……瑠依さんを説得……\n分かった、考えてみる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Use my knowledge of idols… to convince Rui-san…\nAlright‚ I'll think about it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依さんのプロフィールは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "天動瑠依、十七歳……高校二年生……\n11月11日生まれ、蠍座……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "17 years old… a second-year high school student…\nBorn on November 11th‚ a Scorpio…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "身長165センチ、体重46キロ……\nスリーサイズは上から84、56、84……\n一人っ子、右利き、性格は努力家……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "165 cm tall‚ weighs 46 kg…\nMeasurements from the top are 84‚ 56‚ 84…\nOnly child‚ right-handed‚ very hard-working…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "好きなものはアイドルとグミ……苦手なものは牛肉……\n特にグミ好きは有名で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She loves idols and gummies… but dislikes beef…\nEspecially known for loving gummies…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルの三人で鍋の具材を持ち寄った時\n鍋にグミを入れたというエピソードも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's a story about when TRINITYAiLE brought ingredients for a hot pot‚\nshe added gummies to it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "急にアイドルオタクのスイッチが入ったな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You suddenly switched on your idol otaku mode‚ huh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "これらの情報から思いつく作戦……それは！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From this information‚ the plan I've come up with is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "国産フルーツの果汁を贅沢に使った\n芳醇な味わいが評判の最高級グミを見せて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Show her the most luxurious gummies\nmade with domestic fruit juice…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "「これがほしければ私とユニットを組んで」と迫る……\nグミ好きな瑠依さんなら、きっとイチコロ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And say‚ \"If you want these‚ form a unit with me\"…\nWith Rui-san's love for gummies‚ she'll surely be tempted…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "こらこらイチコロじゃない。もっと他に方法があるだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not all about this. There's probably another way",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "他に方法……ある？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Another way… is there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "どうして疑問形なんだ？　そもそも雫はなぜ\n天動さんとユニットを組みたいと思ったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why the questioning tone? Why did you\nwant to form a unit with Tendo-san in the first place?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk019.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依さんは……最初は、テレビでよく観ていた\n憧れのアイドルの一人だった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-san was… an idol I often watched on TV at first…\nShe was one of the idols I admired…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk020.m4a",
      "text": "それから……本人に初めて会って……\nパフォーマンスを間近で見て、圧倒された……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then… when I met her in person…\nI was blown away by her performance up close…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk021.m4a",
      "text": "そのパフォーマンスが……\nもの凄い練習量で努力してきた成果だと知って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Knowing that her performance\ncame from intense practice and effort…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk022.m4a",
      "text": "前からファンだったけど、もっと好きになった……\n瑠依さんを、もっと応援したくなった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been a fan for a while‚ but I came to like her even more…\nI wanted to support Rui-san even more…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "自分がアイドルになっても\n好きなアイドルを応援したいなんて雫らしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wanting to support your favorite idol\neven after becoming one yourself‚ that's so like you‚ Shizuku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk023.m4a",
      "text": "私は自分に自信がなかった……だから……\n自信を持ってステージに立つ瑠依さんに憧れた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't have confidence in myself… That's why…\nI admired Rui-san‚ who stood on the stage with such confidence…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk024.m4a",
      "text": "堂々としたたたずまい……\n自分を追い込むストイックさ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her majestic presence…\nHer stoic drive to push herself…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk025.m4a",
      "text": "笑顔を絶やさないファンサービスや……\n芸能人としての存在感やオーラまで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her ever-present smile and fan service…\nTo the very aura and presence she has as an entertainer…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk026.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依さんはアイドルに必要なものを沢山持ってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-san has everything an idol needs…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk027.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依さんは私の憧れで、目標とするアイドルの一人……\nだから私は……誰かと組むなら、瑠依さんがいい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-san is one of the idols I look up to and aim to be like…\nThat's why… if I were to pair up with anyone‚ I'd want it to be Rui-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 250.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk028.m4a",
      "text": "私は瑠依さんと一緒に歌いたい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to sing alongside Rui-san…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "その想いをそのまま伝えてみたらどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why don't you just express your feelings?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 261.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "素直な気持ちをまっすぐにぶつければ\n天動さんも真剣に話を聞いてくれるはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you sincerely express your feelings‚\nI'm sure Tendo-san will listen seriously.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 267.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk029.m4a",
      "text": "私の本音を……瑠依さんにぶつける……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Express my true feelings to Rui-san…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk030.m4a",
      "text": "でも、実はファンだとか……ずっと憧れてたとか……\n限界オタクの一人語り……ドン引きされない……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if I tell her I've been a fan and always admired her…\nA monologue of a limitless otaku…will you not be turned off…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 280.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "天動さんは一生懸命な人を見下したりしないよ\nそれは雫もよく知ってるだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tendo-san wouldn't look down on someone who's sincere.\nYou know that too‚ don't you‚ Shizuku?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 288.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk031.m4a",
      "text": "うん……知ってる……\n分かった……思い切って、当たって砕けてみる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… I know…\nI get it…I'll take the plunge and try to break it…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 295.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "そこは砕けないようにな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't let it break",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 300.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk032.m4a",
      "text": "ん……言い方、間違えた……\n思い切って、瑠依さんに気持ちをぶつけてみる……！",
      "translations": {
